7T14:41:00+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572584912"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572584912"&gt;上星六去沙頭角遊覽，申請咗禁區紙但唔俾入中英街。唯有去旁邊間酒家撐枱腳，因為二樓露台可以影到相。原本以為只賣遊客菜式，但食落碟頭粉麵飯嘅質素都唔錯，價錢亦算公道。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;封面&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16256472" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572584912" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250527/20250527_182424e165d527dd9a9feAq6fXZxebRW.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/710445/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250527/20250527_182424e165d527dd9a9feAq6fXZxebRW.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16256472_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16256472&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250524_135938_HDR.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (98.93 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-27 14:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;幾好味，豬肉有肥有瘦炆得腍，配料主要係蔥同薑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16256473" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572584912" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250527/20250527_eefed966872685901bb4MPZyV9Vk8n0q.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/adaf4d/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250527/20250527_eefed966872685901bb4MPZyV9Vk8n0q.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16256473_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src=